---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const title = "SEO & Web Design Blog | Self Labs Web Design";
const description = "Expert insights on SEO, web design, and digital marketing. Learn proven strategies to improve your website's performance and search rankings.";
const canonical = "https://self-labs.io/blog";
---

<BaseLayout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonical={canonical}
  ogImage="/blog/blog-index.jpg"
  ogType="website"
>
  <main class="px-4 py-16 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <!-- Blog Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          SEO & Web Design Blog
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Get the latest insights on SEO, web design, and digital marketing. Learn proven strategies that actually work from someone who's been in the trenches for over 5 years.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href="/rss.xml" class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M3.429 2.571c-1.143 0-2.071.928-2.071 2.071s.928 2.071 2.071 2.071 2.071-.928 2.071-2.071-.928-2.071-2.071-2.071zm0 5.143c-1.143 0-2.071.928-2.071 2.071s.928 2.071 2.071 2.071 2.071-.928 2.071-2.071-.928-2.071-2.071-2.071zm0 5.143c-1.143 0-2.071.928-2.071 2.071s.928 2.071 2.071 2.071 2.071-.928 2.071-2.071-.928-2.071-2.071-2.071z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Subscribe to RSS Feed</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured Post -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Latest Post</h2>
        <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-orange-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-2xl">
              SEO
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
                <a href="/blog/seo-best-practices-2025" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">
                  10 Essential SEO Best Practices for 2025
                </a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                Look, I've been doing SEO for over 5 years now, and I've seen what actually works. These aren't just theories - these are the proven strategies that'll boost your rankings and drive real traffic to your site.
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span>By Will Sargent</span>
                <span>•</span>
                <span>Dec 19, 2024</span>
                <span>•</span>
                <span>10 min read</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- All Blog Posts -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">All Posts</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Blog Post 1 -->
          <article class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4">
              SEO
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
              <a href="/blog/seo-best-practices-2025" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">
                10 Essential SEO Best Practices for 2025
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              The proven strategies that'll boost your rankings and drive real traffic to your site. No fluff, just results.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-400">
              <span>Dec 19, 2024</span>
              <span>10 min read</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Blog Post 2 -->
          <article class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4">
              CWV
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
              <a href="/blog/core-web-vitals-guide" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">
                Core Web Vitals: Complete Guide to Website Performance
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              Let me be straight with you - if your website's slow, you're losing customers. Here's how to fix them.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-400">
              <span>Dec 19, 2024</span>
              <span>12 min read</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Blog Post 3 -->
          <article class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4">
              RWD
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
              <a href="/blog/responsive-web-design-seo" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">
                Responsive Web Design SEO: Mobile-First Optimization Guide
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              Here's a harsh truth: if your website doesn't work on mobile, you're basically invisible to Google.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-400">
              <span>Dec 19, 2024</span>
              <span>15 min read</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Blog Post 4 -->
          <article class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4">
              SPD
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
              <a href="/blog/website-speed-optimization" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">
                Website Speed Optimization: 15 Techniques That Actually Work
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              Your website's slow, and it's killing your business. Every second of delay costs you customers and rankings.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-400">
              <span>Dec 19, 2024</span>
              <span>18 min read</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Blog Post 5 -->
          <article class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4">
              DES
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
              <a href="/blog/seo-for-web-designers" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">
                SEO for Web Designers: Technical Implementation Guide
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              Look, I get it - you're a designer, not an SEO expert. But here's the thing: if you're not thinking about SEO when you design...
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-400">
              <span>Dec 19, 2024</span>
              <span>14 min read</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Blog Post 6 -->
          <article class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4">
              INT
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
              <a href="/blog/website-design-seo-integration" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">
                Website Design & SEO: Complete Integration Guide
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              Here's the secret most agencies don't want you to know: the best websites aren't just beautiful or just SEO-optimized...
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-gray-400">
              <span>Dec 19, 2024</span>
              <span>20 min read</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20 p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Stop Guessing and Start Ranking?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          I've helped over 200 businesses get their websites ranking on page 1 of Google. Want to be next? Let's talk about how we can get your site performing better.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-orange-500 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-600 transition-colors">
            Get Your Free SEO Audit
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+1-943-234-9570" class="border border-orange-500 text-orange-500 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-500/10 transition-colors">
            Call: (943) 234-9570
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
